[["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]","Former Southgate Police Lt. and city Information Technology Director Scott Hayes, 47, died earlyÂ  Saturday morning after he was involved in a car accident."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/p[2]/text()[2]","He was traveling on Allen Road near Pennsylvania in Brownstown Township at about 3:30 a.m. when his car struck the rear of a trailer pulled by a semitruck."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/p[2]/text()[3]","Details of the crash were not released pending further investigation of the incident."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/p[2]/text()[4]","Hayes served nearly 21 years in the Southgate Police Department, and another two years as the city IT director before taking a job with the Detroit Police Department in 2010."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/text()[6]","\n\n                            "],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]","In Detroit he worked as the Director of Technical Services and most recently as the Director of Public Safety and Cyber Security, a position he was promoted to in Nov."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/p[3]/text()[2]","Funeral services are being handled by Michigan Memorial Funeral Home in New Boston."],["/html[1]/body[1]/div[4]/div[4]/div[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]/p[3]/text()[3]","A viewing will be held Wednesday from 5 to 8 p.m. and Thursday from noon to 8 p.m. The funeral service is scheduled for 11 a.m. Friday. "]]